            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <p xml:lang="heb">תתנח נפשה<lb/>דאיפי בר ש<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="2"/>
               <lb/>מארס דמית<lb/>ראיש ירח אל<supplied reason="lost">ול</supplied>
               <lb/>דשתה דשבעה<lb/>דשמיטה ו<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="2"/>
               <lb/>שתת <gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="1"/> מי<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/>
               <lb/>
               <gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="1"/> וא ש<supplied reason="lost">נין</supplied>
            </p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>May the soul be rested<lb/>of 'YPY son of SH..<lb/>M'RS who died<lb/>at the
                    beginning of the month El[ul],<lb/>in the seventh year<lb/>of the sabbatical
                    cycle...<lb/>?<lb/>. and 1 years.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p> The ה of line 5 and the ס of line 3 are in parentheses, added by editor, for no
                    clear reason. </p>
            </div>
